ography information for Jonathan Ashworth","Leicester South","Jonathan Ashworth","119599"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806524","Cabinet Office","false","2017-12-19","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p>","Kingswood","Chris Skidmore",,"2017-12-19T15:41:18.67Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806524/answer","Biography information for Chris Skidmore","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806524/answer","PQ119600 Jonathan Asworth ( OW) .pdf","PQ119600 Jonathan Asworth ( OW) .pdf","UKSA Response ","UKSA Response ","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806524/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2017-12-14","Death: Weather","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many excess winter deaths there were in England in each year since 1997.","false","Biography information for Jonathan Ashworth","Leicester South","Jonathan Ashworth","119600"
