"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806621","Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","false","2017-12-20","<p>The Secretary of State regularly meets honourable members from across the house to discuss a range of issues.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>","Camborne and Redruth","George Eustice","119699","2017-12-20T13:08:26.113Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806621/answer","Biography information for George Eustice","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806621/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806621/answer",,,,,"13","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","2017-12-14","Fisheries: Quotas","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs, when he last met the hon. Member for Aberdeen South to discuss fishing quotas.","false","Biography information for Alan Brown","Kilmarnock and Loudoun","Alan Brown","119697"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806622","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2017-12-21","<p>I have not discussed this issue with my Indonesian counterpart. However, during his visit to Papua in mid-November, the UK Ambassador to Indonesia, Moazzam Malik, met local government officials, civil society groups, businesses and local communities. He raised a range of human rights issues, including freedom of expression and association, media access, and the resolution of past human rights cases. The UK Government fully respects the territorial integrity of Indonesia.</p>","Cities of London and Westminster","Mark Field",,"2017-12-21T16:53:08.833Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806622/answer","Biography information for Mark Field","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806622/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806622/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2017-12-14","Papua: Freedom of Association","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, what representations he has made to his Indonesian counterpart on the right to freedom of association for members of the United Liberation Movement for West Papua in that country.","false","Biography information for Alex Sobel","Leeds North West","Alex Sobel","119698"
